Dialogs.Dialog: Aren't we a little bit distant？ I wonder...
Is it okay if I stay by your side...？
Hey, can I stand next to you？
Hey... Can I get closer to you？
Can you come a little closer to me...？
It's okay if I get closer to you, right？
Well then... I'll be at your side.
I'll be next to you, okay？
Hehe, let's shrink the distance between us.
It's better if the distance between us disappears.
I want to feel you more...
I don't even want us to be a millimeter apart...
H-Hey... Why're you getting so close all of a sudden？
You'll hear my heartbeats like this...
You know that you're so close to me, right...？
...If you get so close to me, I won't know what to do.
Aren't we still a little bit distant？ I wonder...
I don't mind that we're so close...
Yeah... We are lovers, after all.
Being so close to you must be a privilege given only to me, right？
I don't mind doing things you want to do...
Closer... Can you come closer to me？
Even though I've mustered my bravery...
I hope you really could understand...
Hey, even though I had high expectations...
Ah, well... I'm not ready for this...
Wait, just a little bit... okay？
Hehe... What do you intend to do？
Hehe... I'll forgive you this time.
One more time... Do you dislike it？
What will happen to me if you do this？
Don't look at me like that...
It's just me... This is not fair.
I'm feeling awkward... Can I go over there？
I'm happy... I'm so happy, you know？
Will you do this again next time？
What do you intend to do？ Hey...
If you don't hurry, I will do...
Hey... You know what to do, right？
Did I do something to hurt your feelings？
Don't you want to kiss me？
What should I do to put you in the mood...？
Just a little bit more... okay？
Some more would be fine, right？
I can't let you stop now.
Hey, once more... Is it okay？
Can you do it once more？
I didn't tell you to stop, did I...？
What should I do？ That wasn't enough...
You can do whatever you want...
I want to know more about you...
I want to feel your touch on my skin...
I want to be with you like this, forever...
Is it all right to feel this happy？
It feels like I'm beaming with happiness...
It feels like I cannot do anything if you're not with me...
Will you be by my side forever？
I can't think of a world without you...
It's all right as long as I have you by my side...
As long as you're by my side, I...
I love you more than anything else...
I don't want to be separated from you...
I like it when you kiss me...
...Yeah, I think I like it... when you kiss me.
Let's do it again next time, okay？
Kissing makes you feel happy, don't you think？
You make my heart skip a beat...
Do you feel like we should have more time for the kisses...？
If I say I don't want to be separated from you, will it trouble you？
I'm so happy. I'm even crying...
Having you here with me is my ultimate happiness...
Let's wait till the next chance, okay？
Let's wait till next time, okay？
How about next time...？ Yeah, okay...
We can do this next time, right？
Shall I expect something more on our next date？
I love you... I love you so much.
This feeling... How can I make you understand？
I love you... with all my heart.
A kiss... Can we do it again？
Next time, I want a kiss just like today's.
Later on, we should do this more often, okay？
Hey, I don't know when but... I want to be your bride... Oh well...
Someday, I want to be your bride...
I want to walk by your side... Someday... Down the aisle...
Someday... We can do more, right...？
I wish we could stay like this a little longer...
If I become addicted to this, it's all your fault.
I haven't had enough from you...
Oh, I can't believe that I'm this happy. I'm so happy that you are with me right here, right now.
I'll try my best because I want to always be by your side.
Let's be together like this forever, okay？ I'll always... always... love you.
